<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A1406037002">
<title>
Connecting Rod Bearing General Information
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Service connecting rod bearings are available in standard size and 0.25 mm undersize bearing, and standard size bearing has 5 kinds of bearings differing in tolerance.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
For identification of undersize bearing, it is painted red at the position as indicated in figure, undersize bearing thickness is 1.605 – 1.615 mm (0.0632 – 0.0636 in.) at its center.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01140164.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "41.010mm" ver = "01" gw = "155" gh = "99"/>
